                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9756" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1468</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1075 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">逆境重生，“摘星”归来——步步高破产重整之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Reborn in Adversity and Return with&quot;Delisting the Risk Alert&quot;——The Road to Bankruptcy Reorganization of the Better life</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">李金茹，韩子轩，史雅杰，魏天翼，杜金铭，程验涵，田晶晶</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">天津科技大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">步步高商业连锁股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">贸易与金融业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">14 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">破产重整；重整原因；重整措施；步步高</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Insolvency Reorganization; Reorganization Motives; Reorganization Method;the Better life</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">随着经济持续快速增长，居民收入水平不断提高，居民的消费能力和消费意愿也同步增强，零售市场迎来发展机遇。步步高集团抓住这一机遇，实现迅猛发展，于2008年成功在深交所上市，成为民营商超第一股。然而，在电商行业快速崛起冲击传统零售业态的背景下，叠加企业自身盲目扩张、业务转型受阻及房地产投资失利等多重因素，步步高逐渐陷入经营困境，最终因资不抵债于2023年10月经债权人龙牌食品申请进入破产重整程序。本案例展示步步高发展历程与破产重整全过程，包括国资注入、寻找产业投资人、引入胖东来管理团队以及经营策略调整等。通过案例的展示，引导学生思考步步高破产重整的原因、步步高重整的方式以及具体措施，帮助学生全面了解破产重整程序，思考重整后将会面临的风险与问题，并为行业中陷入相同困境的公司提供参考。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">With the sustained and rapid economic growth, the income level of residents has been constantly rising, and their consumption capacity and willingness have also been increasing simultaneously. The retail market has thus witnessed a golden opportunity. The Better life seized this opportunity and achieved rapid development. In 2008, it successfully listed on the Shenzhen Stock Exchange, becoming the first private supermarket company to go public.However, in the context of the rapid rise of the e-commerce industry, which has impacted traditional retail formats, coupled with the company&#39;s own blind expansion, blocked business transformation, and failed real estate investments, the Better life gradually fell into an operational predicament. Eventually, due to insolvency, it entered the bankruptcy reorganization process in September 2024 upon the application of creditor Longpai Food. This case presents the entire development process and bankruptcy reorganization of the Better life, including the injection of state-owned capital, the search for industrial investors, the introduction of the management team from Pang Donglai, and the adjustment of business strategies. Through the presentation of this case, students are guided to think about the reasons for the Better life&#39;s bankruptcy reorganization, the methods and specific measures of its reorganization, and to gain a comprehensive understanding of the bankruptcy reorganization process. It also prompts them to consider the risks and issues that may arise after reorganization and provides a reference for companies in the industry facing similar predicaments.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《财务管理理论与实务》《财务会计理论与实务》《企业重组与并购》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">企业破产重组的动因；企业破产重整措施；破产重整的效果分析；破产重整的风险</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-08</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
